                <br /><br />                               
                <p>After a successful experience in a cozy restaurant setting, Giovanni&rsquo;s Bistro is growing.</p>
                <p>By early September, this exciting dining spot will increase in size with more seating and a larger bar. </p>
                <p>The first thing you notice when you enter Giovanni&rsquo;s Bistro Bar and Catering on Springfield Avenue in Berkeley Heights might just be the d&eacute;cor. Linens in soft, easy shades of lavender tell you this isn&rsquo;t just another &ldquo;white tablecloth&rdquo; dining experience. There&rsquo;s something different about Giovanni&rsquo;s &ndash; casual yet elegant, upscale yet welcoming, with a husband-and-wife ownership team who built the bistro as a passion project of sorts after fulfilling careers in other fields. At Giovanni&rsquo;s, the name of the game is customer service and guest satisfaction &ndash; which only makes the outstanding food taste that much better!</p>
